                                <p>
                                    Dear Delegates,
                                </p>
                                <p>It is with immense pleasure that I welcome you the International Press Corps of the DSMUN ’16.</p>
                                <p>For introductions, I am currently pursuing the IB Diploma Programme in Class 12. Besides taking part in MUNs, I serve as the Editor for three of my School’s publications, hence the affinity for International Press. Outside the classroom, I play the Piano and represent my School in Football and Hockey.</p>
                                <p>Coming to the Conference: this year, the working procedure of the committee has been revamped. As a delegate, you are no longer expected to write a mere commentary on the proceedings of the allotted committee. As a delegate representing an International News Agency, you are expected to digitally execute the following:</p>
                                <p><ul>
                                    <li><b>A thorough analysis of the issue being discussed in your committee. You will be expected to commit thorough research on the respective agendas of your allotted committees in order to formulate your analysis. </b></li>
                                    <li><b>Written evaluation of the measures being discussed and promulgated in your allotted committees.</b></li>
                                    <li><b>Use of Op-Eds and transcribed Interviews supplemented with images to form and communicate not only your opinions but also perspectives of the delegates present in the committee.</b></li>
                                </ul></p>
                                <p>Further detailed information including Standardizations and Citation Policy will be provided in the Background Guide.</p>
                                <p>The power of Media in today’s day and age is unimaginable. The influence it has over fact, thought, opinion and judgment is immense. It is your duty as a delegate to harness this power to construct opinions and analyses which will have substantial value. You will be judged on the value of your piece and the writing skill you have employed to posit the value. I hope that I will have privilege to peruse some brilliant pieces of writing.</p>
                                <p>I will be looking forward to meet you all in August.</p>
